### Hadith 2:266

*Narrated 'Abdullah bin 'Umar Abu,*

I offered with Allah's Apostle a two Rakat prayer before the Zuhr prayer
and two Rakat after the Zuhr prayer, two Rakat after Jumua, Maghrib and
'Isha' prayers.

